    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that it's risky but my doctor is always so vague about it. i just want to know if there's actually a way to do it. like if i really leaned into the greens and the garlic, could that actually keep my blood thin enough so i dont have to worry about the warfarin anymore? i just want a natural way to manage it.",
